name: Sleep Seduction: The Beginning: Book One
description: Meet Rose, a maidservant with a secret. Raised during antebellum Louisiana era and living on plantation. She fosters relationships in her home while finding her true love. With her newfound talent to heal herself and others, she is useful to many. Suddenly, she is up rooted from the home she has always known, with her surrogate mother and thrown into a seedy Virginia town. How can she protect herself, while teaching her own child about life and love? Can she prepare her self for the obstacles that lay ahead?
